                        </div>
                        <div class="project-links">
                            <a href="https://github.com/chark1es/cse134b-hw2"
                                >GitHub</a
                            >
                            <a href="https://cse134b-hw2-cmn010.netlify.app"
                                >Live Site</a
                            >
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="project-card">
                    <img
                        src="./thumbnails/wireframe.webp"
                        alt="Initial wireframe design showing the layout planning for the website"
                        width="600"
                        height="400"
                        loading="lazy"
                    />
                    <div class="project-content">
                        <h3>Initial Wireframe</h3>
                        <p>
                            This is the initial wireframe for the website. It
                            has obviously changed since then lol.
                        </p>
                        <div class="project-links">
                            <a href="./thumbnails/wireframe.webp"
